If I drank Fanta, would I be Fantastic….? Because I definitely drink alcohol….?
My other half says I'm a beer snob - I'm ok with that. Making mead and the occasional beer at the moment.
Give me Porters.. Give me Stouts!! Keep the sours to yourself...

Keeping my friends close,
 but my beers closer.
Drinky drinky, time for less thinky.
